{"tid":201881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沉住氣， 切勿受人挑釁","createTime":"2017-04-15T06:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T09:04:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46b5126ab7c6bcd5f50ddde4463c94c18d7a9839","tid":201881,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"沉住氣， 切勿受人挑釁<br />\n<br />\n如何識別打手？<br />\n<br />\n1. 不斷出分化post<br />\n2. 舉出極on9、極易被反駁的論點，引人去屌佢<br />\n3. 舉出無任何事實支持的論點<br />\n4. 當有相反意見時，只標籤「青症」「打手」「五毛」「熱狗」「食熱狗」等字眼而無辯駁陳述<br />\n5. 不斷以人身攻擊挑釁其他人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打手通常不會單獨出現，因一隻手係拍唔響，當有兩派持極端立場既人係到互屌，大家都知咩事啦，當中一定有幾個係到煽風點火，引你加入戰團做成推post洗版效果。"},{"pid":"4cc02e4aebb555f6d79f19fe53b58d686d88e2e4","tid":201881,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"其實而家已經成功左一半 正常post上返面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692f58e0a0c3e598ae79fc5f510c4e3715ea1b86","tid":201881,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb173a3e296728f6790ccddb0bd83bca63a4ed45","tid":201881,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bf50d839db256848a5568a6780a1d4b5901f33","tid":201881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"記住記住記住,   洗手洗手洗手<br />\n<br />\n引你 加入戰團/回覆 做成推post洗版效果"}]}